{"tid":1127082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭電訊商KPN   排除讓華為建立5G核心網絡","createTime":"2019-04-26T22:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T00:59:33.000Z","uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"99dda1001193ed80e0add9e0a19b4188876149ec","tid":1127082,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T22:44:02.000Z","msg":"荷蘭最大電訊商皇家電訊KPN表示，會選擇西方國家的電訊設備公司建立5G核心網絡。<br />\n<br />\n今次是首間歐洲電訊公司表明排除中國電訊商華為，建立5G核心網絡。KPN指，考慮到荷蘭政界的辯論及關注保護重要基礎設施，及因應荷蘭未來的電訊政策等因素，而作出這個決定。<br />\n<br />\n華為過去十年都是KPN主要的設備供應商，KPN表示，在建立5G的周邊電訊設備仍然會使用華為的產品，現時與華為簽的協議可以因應政府未來的政策而調整或撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5cc2fe79e60383bc0acaf037/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5cc2fe79e60383bc0acaf037%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=3ab3fd72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5cc2fe79e60383bc0acaf037/</a>"},{"pid":"7e251c46b6b54a2d238d53e7c26439a2daf9093b","tid":1127082,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T22:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c322f8137577654efd7872e0e656212b6a23dc92","tid":1127082,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T23:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔怕, 仲有戴露<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cce7ceb8bffe0d5cd4b8007613bbcb8c548ac0","tid":1127082,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"多謝有個傻仔好大喜功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79e8e1934d462bf31e8ccd1cc23877999cf33ae","tid":1127082,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79cce7ceb8bffe0d5cd4b8007613bbcb8c548ac0","tid":1127082,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-